Second Department,

March, 1967 *

(March 15, 1967) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Horatious Jackson, Relator, v. Warden, New York City Correctional Institution for Men (Rikers Island), Respondent.

Not published with other decisions of March, 1967, 27 A D 2d 835. — Rep.

Application for a writ of habeas corpus denied. Beldock, P. J., Christ, Rabin, Benjamin and Munder, JJ., concur.
